      "text": "The last 30 files from the previous sessions which were\nplaced in the agent's folder are preserved here.\nIt's useful for catching up on what has been done\nrecently, correcting mistakes, gathering context on\nrecent tasks and auditing.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
